---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../components/Text.astro";

import typographyDesktop from "../assets/typography/typography-desktop.png";
import typographyTablet from "../assets/typography/typography-tablet.png";
import typographyMobile from "../assets/typography/typography-mobile.png";
---

<section class=`typography-section`>
  <div class="info-block">
    <Heading level={1} class="title">
      <span class="num">05</span> Typography
    </Heading>

    <div class="right">
      <div class="text-block">
        <Text color="grey">
          Redo’s typography balances clarity and professionalism with a modern
          yet timeless type pairing, reinforcing our commitment to accuracy,
          efficiency, and financial stability.
        </Text>
      </div>

      <picture>
        <source srcset={typographyMobile.src} media="(max-width: 799px)" />
        <source srcset={typographyTablet.src} media="(max-width: 1279px)" />
        <!-- Десктоп по умолчанию -->
        <Image
          src={typographyDesktop}
          alt={"Redo Typography"}
          width={467}
          height={300}
          loading="lazy"
          class="image"
        />
      </picture>
      <div class="text-block">
        <Text color="grey">
          Primary Sans-Serif <span class="text-orange">(Rethink Sans Reg)</span>
          is a clean, modern sans-serif typeface that ensures legibility and precision
          across all digital and print materials. Its geometric structure reflects
          clarity, efficiency, and trust, making it the ideal choice for data-heavy
          content, dashboards, and user interfaces.
        </Text>

        <Text color="grey">
          Secondary Serif <span class="text-orange">(Hedvig Letters Serif)</span
          > is a refined, authoritative serif font that adds a touch of tradition
          and credibility. Used for emphasis in headlines, reports, and financial
          documents, it reinforces Redo’s expertise and reliability in correcting
          financial discrepancies.
        </Text>

        <Text color="grey">
          This sans-serif and serif combination creates a dynamic
          contrast—modern yet trustworthy, analytical yet approachable, ensuring
          Redo’s brand communication is always clear, professional, and
          dependable.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class=""></div>
  <div class="type-styles">
    <div class="typefaces">
      <div class="typeface">
        <Text variant="default">Primary Typeface</Text>
        <div class="typeface-primary">Rethink Sans Reg</div>
      </div>
      <div class="typeface">
        <Text variant="default">Secondary Typeface</Text>
        <div class="typeface-secondary">Hedvig Letters Serif</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sizing">
      <div class="header">
        <Heading level={3} class="title"> Sizing </Heading>
        <Text color="grey"
          >Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
          eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad
          minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
          aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .typography-section {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--divider, #e6e6e6);
      padding: 32px 32px 128px 32px;

      gap: 30px;
    }

    .info-block {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .title .num {
      color: var(--accent-2, #f45f00);
      font: inherit; /* размер/вес как у H1 */
    }

    .text-orange {
      color: var(--accent-2, #f45f00);
    }
    .right {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .right .text-block {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .photo {
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .type-styles {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 100px;
      padding: 0 32px;
    }

    .typefaces {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .typeface {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .typeface-primary {
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 60px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 130%;
    }

    .typeface-secondary {
      font-family: "Hedvig Letters Serif", arial;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 60px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 130%;
    }

    .sizing {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .header {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
      padding: 32px 0 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--divider, #e6e6e6);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1279px) and (min-width: 800px) {
      .typography-section {
        padding: 88px 20px;
      }
      .image {
        object-fit: cover;
        max-width: 352px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 799px) {
      .typography-section {
        padding: 32px 20px 80px 20px;
      }
      .info-block {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .image {
        object-fit: cover;
        max-width: 335px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
